---
import MainLayout from "@/layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import { SITE } from "@data/constants";

const pageTitle: string = `Privacy Policy & Terms and Conditions | ${SITE.title}`;
---

<MainLayout title={pageTitle}>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-14">
    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <h1>Privacy Policy & Terms and Conditions</h1>
      <p>Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>
      <p>These terms and policies apply to your use of the website and services provided by <strong>KRAFFE MAKİNA MÜHENDİSLİK İNŞAAT SANAYİ VE TİCARET ANONİM ŞİRKETİ</strong> (hereinafter referred to as "Kraffe Roasters", "we", "us", or "our").</p>

      <hr />

      <h2>Part 1: Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p>At Kraffe Roasters, we are committed to protecting the privacy of our visitors, customers, and business partners. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information[cite: 10, 11].</p>

      <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
      <p>When you interact with us through our website or communication channels, we may collect the following personal data[cite: 11, 12]:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Full name [cite: 12]</li>
        <li>Email address [cite: 12]</li>
        <li>Phone number [cite: 12]</li>
        <li>Company name and your position [cite: 12]</li>
        <li>Country or city of residence [cite: 12]</li>
        <li>Product or service inquiries [cite: 12]</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
      <p>Your personal data is strictly used for legitimate business purposes[cite: 12], which include:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Responding to your inquiries and contact requests [cite: 12]</li>
        <li>Sending you quotations, product details, or service offers [cite: 12]</li>
        <li>Providing pre-sales and after-sales support [cite: 12]</li>
        <li>Improving our website, services, and overall user experience [cite: 12]</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not sell, rent, or misuse your personal information under any circumstances[cite: 12].</p>

      <h3>3. Data Security</h3>
      <p>Your personal information is stored on secure servers and protected against unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure[cite: 13]. All sensitive data transmissions are encrypted using SSL technology[cite: 14].</p>

      <h3>4. Third-Party Services</h3>
      <p>We may use trusted third-party tools (such as Google Ads, Google Analytics) to optimize our website traffic and advertising efforts[cite: 16]. These tools may collect anonymous usage data governed by their respective privacy policies[cite: 17]. For detailed information on how we use cookies, please refer to our <a href="/cookie-policy">Cookie Policy</a>[cite: 15].</p>

      <h3>5. Your Rights</h3>
      <p>You have the right to[cite: 18]:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Request access to the personal data we hold about you [cite: 18]</li>
        <li>Ask for corrections or deletion of your information [cite: 18]</li>
        <li>Withdraw your consent for future marketing communications at any time [cite: 18]</li>
      </ul>

      <hr />

      <h2>Part 2: Terms & Conditions</h2>
      <p>The following terms govern your use of the Kraffe Roasters website and our services.</p>

      <h3>1. Acceptance of Terms</h3>
      <p>By accessing or using our website and services, you agree to be bound by these Terms & Conditions. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, please refrain from using our website[cite: 19]. We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time, and your continued use constitutes acceptance of those changes[cite: 20].</p>

      <h3>2. Products and Services</h3>
      <p>All products displayed on our website are subject to availability[cite: 21]. We reserve the right to limit quantities, refuse orders, or discontinue products without prior notice[cite: 22]. Product specifications, prices, and availability are subject to change[cite: 23]. Please note that images are for illustrative purposes only and may differ slightly from the actual products[cite: 24].</p>

      <h3>3. Ordering and Payment</h3>
      <p>By placing an order, you warrant that all information provided is accurate and complete[cite: 25]. An order confirmation email does not constitute legal acceptance; a binding contract is only formed when we dispatch your order[cite: 26]. Payment must be made in full before dispatch[cite: 27]. We accept major credit cards and bank transfers[cite: 27]. All prices are listed in <strong>EUR (€)</strong> and exclude VAT unless otherwise explicitly stated[cite: 28].</p>

      <h3>4. Shipping and Delivery</h3>
      <p>Delivery times are estimates and are not strictly guaranteed. We cannot be held liable for delays beyond our reasonable control[cite: 29]. The risk of loss and title for items purchased pass to you upon delivery[cite: 30]. You are responsible for inspecting the goods upon arrival and must report any physical damage within 48 hours of delivery[cite: 31].</p>

      <h3>5. Warranty</h3>
      <p>All Kraffe Roasters machines come with a standard <strong>2-year manufacturer warranty</strong> covering defects in materials and workmanship[cite: 32]. This warranty does not cover damages resulting from misuse, improper installation, or unauthorized modifications[cite: 33].</p>

      <h3>6. Limitation of Liability</h3>
      <p>To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, Kraffe Roasters shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of our products or services[cite: 34]. Our total liability shall under no circumstances exceed the purchase price of the product giving rise to the claim[cite: 35].</p>

      <h3>7. Governing Law and Jurisdiction</h3>
      <p>These terms and conditions are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of <strong>Turkey</strong>[cite: 36]. Any disputes arising out of or in connection with these terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of <strong>Izmir, Turkey</strong>[cite: 37].</p>

      <hr />

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy & Terms and Conditions, please contact us at[cite: 18]:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@krafferoasters.com">info@krafferoasters.com</a></li>
        <li><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://krafferoasters.com/">https://krafferoasters.com/</a></li>
      </ul>

    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
